You may customize this configuration to allow for replacement of virtually any part of MvcSiteMapProvider by implementing one of its interfaces and injecting an instance of your implementation. This package works best if you don't already have a pre-existing dependency injection configuration in your project.

You may customize this configuration to allow for replacement of virtually any part of MvcSiteMapProvider by implementing one of its interfaces and injecting an instance of your implementation. This package works best if you don't already have a pre-existing dependency injection configuration in your project.
